CopyNumberTableModel::CopyNumberTableModel Synopsis:

DEPRECATED: DMET2 only

This is the TransferObject to the TsvFile DataAccessObject design pattern. There is only ever one of these in existence, i.e. this is a single instance class.

copy number file -> copy number table model

Main constructor to read the copy number report file and stash the data into the model.

Parameters:
rte - Single instance RunTimeEnvironment
cntmFileName - the input file to read.
